_sText:
The level is for Counterstrike source. 

The setting is a brazilian favela where 3 UN aid workers has been captured by the local druggang. 
The brazilian special police BOPE is contacted to solve the problem and get the hostages out.

Alot of the textures are custom also some of the models are custom. All other models are from the original CS/Hl2

Any suggestions on the map can be emailed to me
